title: Jumbo Dino Egg kids toys， Dinosuar Egg Dig Kit For 3+ Year Olds. Educational Science STEM Gift for Children On Christmas, Thanksgiving, Birthday
features: DINO EGG DIG KITS: Jumbo dinosaur eggs , a magnifying glass, 2 brushes, 3 chisels, a hammer, 12 dinosaur cards. Through these you can get a better understanding of dinosaurs.

Easy to dig: Simply dig it out or soften the dinosaur egg by soaking it in water for a few minutes, then carefully chisel away the clay to dig up the dinosaur inside. Once the dinosaurs turn up, simply rinse off the remaining clay and you can go through the study guide to identify the dinosaurs.
Making learning fun: There are 12 learning cards about dinosaurs in full color. With detailed information and a reference picture on the cards.
Educational toys: Improve kids’ hands-on ability and provoke their interest in archaeology. Perfect gifts for kids on Christmas, Thanksgiving Day, and their birthdays.

Commitment: Our dinosaur eggs are made of non-toxic clay materials, which are safe and fun to play with. If you are not satisfied with the kit, please contact our customer support team for a full refund.
